name: Keg Royalties Income Fund (The)
longDescription: The Keg Royalties Income Fund is a Canada-based company. The organization works in the Restaurant business sector. Its primary activity is operating and franchising keg steakhouses and bar restaurants in Canada and the United States. The target market of this company is those people who want a higher-end casual dining experience.
